            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="card-title">About</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <img src="/assets/profile.jpg" class="card-img-top prof-img" alt="Profile Pic">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9 intro">
                            <p>Hi, I am Matt üëã. A self-taught WebDev with a passion for code üíª. I have been self-teaching myself JavaScript, HTML, CSS, NodeJS and React with a strong desire to move into a career in coding üë®‚Äçüíª.</p>
